en.haccp_agreement_body:
Hereby confirms that entering data into the electronic journals and accounting forms of the Restodocks system under their personal account login (login and password) is recognized as equivalent to a handwritten signature in accordance with:

— National legislation on electronic signatures (including Federal Law No. 63-FZ of the Russian Federation and analogous laws of CIS countries);
— International food safety standards (HACCP);
— EAEU Technical Regulation TR CU 021/2011 “On Food Safety”.

The employee undertakes to follow the accounting procedure and not to disclose login credentials.
